description: Global Entertainment Holdings, Inc. operates an independent entertainment content production and distribution company that connects with audiences through compelling motion picture content and social media websites. It produces, finances, and sells motion pictures and other entertainment related content. The company also distributes Hollywood classic movies, TV shows, and shorts and vintage cartoons; develops You've Got The Part, a social media web platform; and operates WeedWeb.com, a professional cannabis network. Global Entertainment Holdings, Inc. was founded in 1996 and is based in Las Vegas, Nevada.
